Retrograde balloon angioplasty of brachiocephalic or common carotid artery 
stenoses at the time of carotid endarterectomy.

Levien LJ(1), Benn CA, Veller MG, Fritz VU.

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgery, University of the Witwatersrand, Johannesburg, South 
